window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>One mistake cost me everything. My gorgeous triton tail was gone, and in its place were the worst things imaginable—tentacles.</p> <p>I’ve learned to live with being different, but now the clock is ticking down to being stuck with them forever. But when a chance presents itself to possibly go back to the way things once were, I can’t pass it up.</p> <p>Along the way, I meet four mates who change my world.</p> <p>The broken wolf. The protective dragon. The passionate griffin. The playful snake.</p> <p>Just when I let myself hope for a happy ending, everything comes crashing down around me. The fate of the world is in the palm of my hand, but to eliminate the threat, I might have to sacrifice more than I’ve bargained for.</p> <p><i>Her Creatures: The Complete Series</i> contains <i>Creature of the Flame</i>, <i>Creature of the Sky</i>, <i>Creature of the Wild</i>, and <i>Creature of the Deep</i>. It contains multiple love interests with an MM relationship. Please see author’s note at beginning of book for content warnings.</p> <p>It is not necessary to listen to any other series before this one. All necessary background on the main character—who briefly appears in the Salinity Cove series when she was younger—will be given throughout this series.</p>"; 
